repo_description: Android and portal backend for My Special Way

schemas.name: query.gql
schemas.content:
type Query {
  students: [Student]
  student(id: ID!): Student

  users: [User]
  user(id: ID!): User

  classes: [Class]!
  classById(id: ID!): Class
  classByName(name: String): Class

  lessons: [Lesson]!

  settings: [Settings]!

  locations: [Location]!
  locationById(id: ID!): Location
  locationsByMapId(image_id: String!, floor: Int): [Location]!
  blockedSections: [BlockedSection]!
  blockedSectionsByLocations(locations: [String]!): [BlockedSection]!

  nonActiveTimes: [NonActiveTime]
}

merged.mergedContent:
# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/9f74163fd3310df62c7fee0f204693e591395f2a/src/modules/graphql/schemas/query.gql:
type Query {
  students: [Student]
  student(id: ID!): Student

  users: [User]
  user(id: ID!): User

  classes: [Class]!
  classById(id: ID!): Class
  classByName(name: String): Class

  lessons: [Lesson]!

  settings: [Settings]!

  locations: [Location]!
  locationById(id: ID!): Location
  locationsByMapId(image_id: String!, floor: Int): [Location]!
  blockedSections: [BlockedSection]!
  blockedSectionsByLocations(locations: [String]!): [BlockedSection]!

  nonActiveTimes: [NonActiveTime]
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/3db6734d3cae1fcfd9ba07c266137d62a4e46c94/src/modules/graphql/schemas/student.gql:
# add full schedule class + student
type Student {
  _id: ID!
  username: String!
  password: String!
  email: String
  firstname: String
  lastname: String
  gender: Gender
  class: Class
  schedule: [TimeSlot!]
  reminders: [Reminder!]
  nonActiveTimes: [NonActiveTime]
  # teacher: Teacher!
}

input InputStudent {
  username: String
  password: String
  email: String
  firstname: String
  lastname: String
  gender: Gender
  class_id: String
  schedule: [InputTimeSlot!]
  reminders: [InputReminder!]
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/3db6734d3cae1fcfd9ba07c266137d62a4e46c94/src/modules/graphql/schemas/user.gql:
type User {
  _id: ID!
  username: String!
  email: String
  firstname: String
  lastname: String
  role: UserType
  gender: Gender
  class: Class
  nonActiveTimes: [NonActiveTime]
}

enum Gender {
  FEMALE
  MALE
}

enum UserType {
  PRINCIPLE
  TEACHER
  STUDENT
}

input InputUser {
  username: String!
  email: String!
  firstname: String!
  lastname: String!
  gender: Gender
  role: UserType!
  class_id: String
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/3dbcb176c39ea9184160ac83f5d0d7b231072f80/src/modules/graphql/schemas/class.gql:
# A type describing a single class
type Class {
  _id: ID!
  name: String!
  grade: String!
  schedule: [TimeSlot]!
  students: [Student]!
}

input InputClass {
    name: String!
    # grade of class /[a-f]/
    grade: String!
    # list of new timeslots on schedule
    schedule: [InputTimeSlot]
}


# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/1df6612dfc9a25f14391f0fc296e15633d9383a1/src/modules/graphql/schemas/lesson.gql:
# A type describing a single lesson for the lessons screen
type Lesson {
  _id: ID!
  title: String!
  icon: String
}

input InputLesson {
    # optional id for when updating schedules
    _id: ID
    title: String!
    icon: String!
}
# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/79283aae266fb5f0dc1987cdc0719a502770b207/src/modules/graphql/schemas/settings.gql:
type Settings {
  _id: ID!
  teachercode: Int
}

input InputSettings {
  teachercode: Int
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/9f74163fd3310df62c7fee0f204693e591395f2a/src/modules/graphql/schemas/location.gql:
# A type that describes a room.
type Location {
  # The location number
  _id: ID!
  # The location name
  name: String
  # location name from the 3D map model
  location_id: String
  # The lat lan cordinates
  position: Point
  icon: String
  type: String
  image_id: String
}

input InputLocation {
  # optional id for when updating schedules
  _id: ID
  name: String
  location_id: String
  position: InputPoint
  icon: String
  type: String
  image_id: String
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/283b437c3341a09bc339fa25d876d864a9fc79f5/src/modules/graphql/schemas/blocked-section.gql:
# A type describing a single blocked section between 2 locations
type BlockedSection {
  _id: ID
  # the reson for blocking this section
  reason: String
  # the from point
  from: String
  # the to point
  to: String
}

input InputBlockedSection {
  reason: String!
  from: String!
  to: String!
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/3db6734d3cae1fcfd9ba07c266137d62a4e46c94/src/modules/graphql/schemas/non-active-time.gql:
# A type describing a single non-active-time for the non-active-time screen
type NonActiveTime {
  _id: ID!
  title: String!
  isAllDayEvent: Boolean!
  startDateTime: String!
  endDateTime: String!
  isAllClassesEvent: Boolean!
  classes: [Class]
}

input InputNonActiveTime {
  title: String!
  isAllDayEvent: Boolean!
  startDateTime: String!
  endDateTime: String!
  isAllClassesEvent: Boolean!
  classesIds: [String]
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/9bb01446d672bc2cb8638759d140dacc14a5703a/src/modules/graphql/schemas/timeslot.gql:
# A type describing a single time slot on the class/student schedule
type TimeSlot {
  # 2 numeric chars (0_0, 0_1...) represents the dayIndex_hourIndex of timeslot grid cell
  index: String!
  hours: String
  original: Original
  lesson: Lesson
  location: Location
  customized: Boolean
}

input InputTimeSlot {
  index: String!
  hours: String
  original: InputOriginal
  lesson: InputLesson!
  location: InputLocation
  customized: Boolean
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/af85b3d7a20b8591edb628302359f78b893bc446/src/modules/graphql/schemas/reminder.gql:
type Reminder {
  enabled: Boolean!
  type: ReminderType
  schedule: [ReminderTime!]
}

input InputReminder {
  enabled: Boolean!
  type: ReminderType
  schedule: [InputReminderTime!]
}

enum ReminderType {
  MEDICINE
  REHAB
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/9be2079cef5636fd83443c8a20e6f8bea395557f/src/modules/graphql/schemas/point.gql:
# A type that describes lat lang cordinates.
type Point {
  floor: Int
}

input InputPoint {
  floor: Int!
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/9bb01446d672bc2cb8638759d140dacc14a5703a/src/modules/graphql/schemas/original.gql:
# A type describing a single time slot on the class/student schedule
type Original {
  # 2 numeric chars (0_0, 0_1...) represents the dayIndex_hourIndex of timeslot grid cell
  expired: String
  lesson: Lesson
  location: Location
}

input InputOriginal {
  expired: String!
  lesson: InputLesson
  location: InputLocation
}

# https://github.com/myspecialway/my-special-way-server/blob/af85b3d7a20b8591edb628302359f78b893bc446/src/modules/graphql/schemas/remindertime.gql:
# A type describing reminder time in student schedule
type ReminderTime {
  # numeric chars (0, 1,...6) represents the dayIndex of remindertime
  daysindex: [Int!]
  hours: [String!]
}

input InputReminderTime {
  daysindex: [Int!]
  hours: [String!]
}
